You can change the decimal format like in this [post](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5054132/how-to-change-the-decimal-separator-of-decimalformat-from-comma-to-dot-point)

    NumberFormat nf = NumberFormat.getNumberInstance(Locale.GERMAN);
